[3]
Date: 22 Dec 2008
From: Anders Bjorkman


We now have 3 patients from Sweden at Karolinska Hospital/Solna and
Huddinge. We are investigating the details of the hotel and locality
involved.

Age / Gender / Hospital of malaria diagnosis / Date of return to
Sweden / Date trip started / Malaria prophylaxis

59 / M / Karolinska-Solna / 18 Nov 2008 / 11 Nov 2008 / No
35 / M / Karolinska-Huddinge / 27 Nov 2008 / 15 Nov 2008 / No
48 / M / Karolinska-Solna / 10 Dec 2008 / 8 Dec 2008 / No

